#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:1
msgid "以股票N天前的价格或数据指标作为选股因子选股基础选股策略，以股票的N日前历史数据作为选股因子，因子排序参数以策略属性的形式控制"
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez les actions en fonction des indicateurs de prix ou de données "
"de l'action il y a N jours comme facteur de sélection des actions. Les "
"données historiques du stock il y a N jours sont utilisées comme facteur de "
"sélection de stock, et les paramètres de tri des facteurs sont contrôlés "
"sous la forme d'attributs de stratégie."

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:4
msgid "``n``: int, 股票历史数据的前置期"
msgstr ""
"``n`` : int, La période de référence des données historiques des actions"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:9 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:8
msgid "在每个选股周期使用N日前的历史数据作为选股因子进行选股"
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez des actions en utilisant les données historiques d'il y a N "
"jours comme facteurs de sélection de titres dans chaque cycle de sélection "
"de titres."

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:11
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:11 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:10
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:11
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:10
msgid "通过以下策略属性控制选股方法:"
msgstr ""
"Contrôlez la méthode de sélection des titres grâce aux attributs de "
"stratégie suivants :"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:13
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:13 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:12
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:13
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:12
msgid ""
"``max_sel_count``:     ``float``,  选股限额，表示最多选出的股票的数量，默认值: ``0.5``，表示选中50%的股票"
msgstr ""
"``max_sel_count``:     ``float``,  Stock selection limit, indicating the "
"maximum number of stocks selected, default value: ``0.5``, indiquant que 50%"
" des actions sont sélectionnées"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:15
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:15 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:14
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:15
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:14
msgid "``condition``:         ``str`` ,   确定股票的筛选条件，默认值``any``"
msgstr ""
"``condition``:         ``str`` ,   Determine the stock screening condition, "
"default value ``any``"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:27
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:27 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:26
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:27
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:26
msgid "``lbound``:            ``float``,  执行条件筛选时的指标下界, 默认值``np.-inf``"
msgstr ""
"``lbound``:            ``float``,  Lower bound of the indicator when "
"executing the condition screening, default value ``np.-inf``"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:29
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:29 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:28
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:29
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:28
msgid "``ubound``:            ``float``,  执行条件筛选时的指标上界, 默认值``np.inf``"
msgstr ""
"``ubound``:            ``float``,  Upper bound of the indicator when "
"executing the condition screening, default value ``np.inf``"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:31
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:31 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:30
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:31
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:30
