msgstr ""
"``sort_ascending``:    ``bool``,   Sorting method, default value: ``False``,"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayAvg:37
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayChange:37 qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayLast:36
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayRateChange:37
#: qteasy.built_in.SelectingNDayVolatility:36
