#: of qteasy.built_in.SellRate:1
msgid "变化率卖出信号策略:"
msgstr "Stratégie de signal de vente de taux de changement."

#: of qteasy.built_in.SellRate:2
msgid "当价格的变化率超过阈值时，产生卖出信号。 本策略不产生买入信号。"
msgstr ""
"Des signaux de vente sont générés lorsque le taux de variation du prix "
"dépasse le seuil. Cette stratégie ne génère pas de signaux d'achat."

#: of qteasy.built_in.BuyRate:6 qteasy.built_in.SellRate:6
msgid "``day``, ``int``, 涨跌幅计算周期"
msgstr "``day`'', ``int`', période de calcul du taux de montée et de descente"

#: of qteasy.built_in.BuyRate:8 qteasy.built_in.SellRate:8
msgid "``change``, ``float``，涨跌幅阈值"
msgstr "``change``, ``float``, seuils haut/bas"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SellRate:12
msgid "在下面情况下产生卖出信号:"
msgstr "Un signal de vente est généré quand."

#: of qteasy.built_in.SellRate:14
msgid "1，当``change`` > 0，且``day``日涨幅大于``change``时，产生-1卖出信号"
msgstr ""
"1, -1 signal de vente généré lorsque ``change`` > 0 and ``day`` daily "
"increase is greater than ``change``"

#: of qteasy.built_in.SellRate:16
msgid "2，当``change`` < 0，且``day``日跌幅大于``change``时，产生-1卖出信号"
msgstr ""
"2, un signal de vente -1 est généré lorsque ``change`` < 0 and the ``day`` "
"daily decline is greater than the ``change``"

