"positions relatives des SMA rapides et lents."

#: of qteasy.built_in.DCRST3:5 qteasy.built_in.DCRSTEMA:5
#: qteasy.built_in.DCRSTRIMA:5 qteasy.built_in.DCRSWMA:5
